data.description: Located in the quiet Hidden Lake community of Vero Beach, Florida, this stunning 3-bedroom home features a versatile den/office space and 2 bathrooms. The spacious kitchen boasts elegant granite countertops, 42-inch cabinets, and modern stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the open floor plan, perfect for gatherings and entertaining. The paver driveway adds to the curb appeal, and with low HOA fees, this home is an excellent value. Plus, you'll be conveniently close to beautiful beaches, shopping, and a variety of restaurants. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream Florida home!
